About the game: PLAY MINE SWEEPING IN THE CUBE EXPANSION(JINGOR FACE)! Jingor Mine is a puzzle game, can be used as a hobby, can challenge intelligence, can be leisure entertainment. In the jingor face, click the left mouse button to open the grid in sweeper mode, and click the left mouse button to mark mines when switching to mine marking mode. Of particular interest is the mines on the other side of an edge in the jingor face.
